ut a binary black\nhole system, and implies that binary black holes finally merge without\naccretion disks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Sep 2010 11:20:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Dec 2010 12:45:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
